{"tid":2166073,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"回應上下議會嘅想法","createTime":"2020-08-20T08:00:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-20T12:05:56.000Z","uid":223407,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a1b5f9a5bc3cfd6a9d6971b3b24e1d3b32c6958b","tid":2166073,"uid":223407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T08:00:51.000Z","msg":"原文見<br />\n組成「二級議會」化解分化毒計，共有10大好處共贏齊探討<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2162332\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2162332</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"violet\">小弟覺得唔係咁可行。原因：<br />\n<br />\n1）人哋下議院係有法律效力。而家呢個民間議會一啲法律效力都冇。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2）你呢個看守議會如果冇35+，基本上係完全冇否決能力。先唔講你未必控制到泛民投乜嘢票。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n某程度上其實呢個安排冇促進到任何政制改革。（如果再加上佢要接受委任嘅話，更加係違憲。）<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n另外，文章係唔係上下級議會掉轉咗？上級議會通常係講貴族（喺香港嘅例子，某程度上就係冇乜民意授權嘅功能組別），下級議會先係有民意授權。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小弟依然支持全體總辭。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"blue\">另外想回應「分化論」：其實講到總辭並留守，有唔同嘅意見本來係好正常，我亦都唔覺得香港人咁容易就會係被分化。每一次有唔同嘅意見，就有人話因住中咗計俾人分化。我更加擔心嘅係，有啲底線同原則，因為怕被分化就守唔住。我哋唔係反對緊中共插手干預香港咩？點解可以支持議員接受委任？而且而家國際咁支持香港人，我哋唔係更加應該把握機會大聲啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"1cfba2094b9145109c962b78c97893f8a70a82dd","tid":2166073,"uid":223407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T08:01:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自推10連"},{"pid":"2cf9444720faa9c0406e5e03b66b555b786f7869","tid":2166073,"uid":223407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T08:01:34.000Z","msg":"1<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c71d2d8a4f6e4a9dfec9bc654bc84ceddada35c","tid":2166073,"uid":223407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T08:01:47.000Z","msg":"2<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b58f533488c38e6ab83173f319b96ed823aed4f","tid":2166073,"uid":223407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T08:01:58.000Z","msg":"3<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07acdffde51cc1151e9f6c9b2fbf03df435f6d19","tid":2166073,"uid":223407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T08:02:13.000Z","msg":"4<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c985336ab0c50f1c1b29c46b2f7e6e75086fe5ae","tid":2166073,"uid":223407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T08:02:27.000Z","msg":"5<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbc660ef6798690c7f7267f73d2cbca93c906e27","tid":2166073,"uid":223407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T08:02:44.000Z","msg":"6<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f4aee122fbc603cb9b9cd72240d3b49acde0767","tid":2166073,"uid":223407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T08:02:59.000Z","msg":"7<img src=\"/assets/fac